title: Delays on M62 motorway after collision
text:
Motorists on M62 in West Yorkshire are facing delays after an accident.
A clear-up is underway the westbound carriageway between junction 26 at Chain Bar and junction 25 for Brighouse.
A lane is also closed between junction 32 at Glass Houghton and junction 31 at Normanton because of a broken down vehicle.
Last updated Thu 17 Sep 2015 Travel West Yorkshire
